{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":3170,"text":"So, stepping down out of the bus,"},{"time":6151,"text":"I headed back to the corner"},{"time":7896,"text":"to head west en route to a braille training session."},{"time":11284,"text":"It was the winter of 2009,"},{"time":13394,"text":"and I had been blind for about a year."},{"time":15815,"text":"Things were going pretty well."},{"time":17948,"text":"Safely reaching the other side,"},{"time":19855,"text":"I turned to the left,"},{"time":21316,"text":"pushed the auto-button for\nthe audible pedestrian signal,"},{"time":23920,"text":"and waited my turn."},{"time":25844,"text":"As it went off, I took off"},{"time":27933,"text":"and safely got to the other side."},{"time":29606,"text":"Stepping onto the sidewalk,"},{"time":31702,"text":"I then heard the sound of a steel chair"},{"time":34396,"text":"slide across the concrete sidewalk in front of me."},{"time":38552,"text":"I know there's a cafe on the corner,"},{"time":40469,"text":"and they have chairs out in front,"},{"time":42115,"text":"so I just adjusted to the left"},{"time":43511,"text":"to get closer to the street."},{"time":45355,"text":"As I did, so slid the chair."},{"time":48995,"text":"I just figured I'd made a mistake,"},{"time":51076,"text":"and went back to the right,"},{"time":52914,"text":"and so slid the chair in perfect synchronicity."},{"time":56409,"text":"Now I was getting a little anxious."},{"time":58774,"text":"I went back to the left,"},{"time":60387,"text":"and so slid the chair,"},{"time":61676,"text":"blocking my path of travel."},{"time":64284,"text":"Now, I was officially freaking out."},{"time":67286,"text":"So I yelled,"},{"time":68871,"text":"\"Who the hell's out there? What's going on?\""},{"time":72132,"text":"Just then, over my shout,"},{"time":74384,"text":"I heard something else, a familiar rattle."},{"time":77069,"text":"It sounded familiar,"},{"time":78915,"text":"and I quickly considered another possibility,"},{"time":80778,"text":"and I reached out with my left hand,"},{"time":82709,"text":"as my fingers brushed against something fuzzy,"},{"time":86113,"text":"and I came across an ear,"},{"time":88664,"text":"the ear of a dog, perhaps a golden retriever."},{"time":92926,"text":"Its leash had been tied to the chair"},{"time":94915,"text":"as her master went in for coffee,"},{"time":96652,"text":"and she was just persistent in her efforts"},{"time":98444,"text":"to greet me, perhaps get a scratch behind the ear."},{"time":101782,"text":"Who knows, maybe she was volunteering for service."},{"time":104394,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":106773,"text":"But that little story is really about"},{"time":109182,"text":"the fears and misconceptions that come along"},{"time":112381,"text":"with the idea of moving through the city"},{"time":115284,"text":"without sight,"},{"time":116607,"text":"seemingly oblivious to the environment"},{"time":119568,"text":"and the people around you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":122468,"text":"So let me step back and set the stage a little bit."},{"time":126369,"text":"On St. Patrick's Day of 2008,"},{"time":128928,"text":"I reported to the hospital for surgery"},{"time":131515,"text":"to remove a brain tumor."},{"time":133709,"text":"The surgery was successful."},{"time":135796,"text":"Two days later, my sight started to fail."},{"time":138965,"text":"On the third day, it was gone."}]},{"cues":[{"time":142487,"text":"Immediately, I was struck by an incredible sense"},{"time":144584,"text":"of fear, of confusion, of vulnerability,"},{"time":148473,"text":"like anybody would."},{"time":150922,"text":"But as I had time to stop and think,"},{"time":153414,"text":"I actually started to realize"},{"time":155165,"text":"I had a lot to be grateful for."},{"time":158089,"text":"In particular, I thought about my dad,"},{"time":161085,"text":"who had passed away from complications"},{"time":163282,"text":"from brain surgery."},{"time":165385,"text":"He was 36. I was seven at the time."},{"time":170476,"text":"So although I had every reason"},{"time":173169,"text":"to be fearful of what was ahead,"},{"time":175401,"text":"and had no clue quite what was going to happen,"},{"time":178035,"text":"I was alive."},{"time":179793,"text":"My son still had his dad."},{"time":182505,"text":"And besides, it's not like I was the first person"},{"time":184392,"text":"ever to lose their sight."},{"time":186005,"text":"I knew there had to be all sorts of systems"},{"time":188154,"text":"and techniques and training to have"},{"time":190471,"text":"to live a full and meaningful, active life"},{"time":193033,"text":"without sight."}]},{"cues":[{"time":194635,"text":"So by the time I was discharged from the hospital"},{"time":196782,"text":"a few days later, I left with a mission,"},{"time":199486,"text":"a mission to get out and get the best training"},{"time":201616,"text":"as quickly as I could and get on to rebuilding my life."},{"time":206780,"text":"Within six months, I had returned to work."},{"time":210828,"text":"My training had started."},{"time":212430,"text":"I even started riding a tandem bike"},{"time":214090,"text":"with my old cycling buddies,"},{"time":215715,"text":"and was commuting to work on my own,"},{"time":218412,"text":"walking through town and taking the bus."},{"time":220887,"text":"It was a lot of hard work."}]},{"cues":[{"time":223650,"text":"But what I didn't anticipate"},{"time":225917,"text":"through that rapid transition"},{"time":228889,"text":"was the incredible experience of the juxtaposition"},{"time":232637,"text":"of my sighted experience\nup against my unsighted experience"},{"time":236577,"text":"of the same places and the same people"},{"time":239250,"text":"within such a short period of time."}]},{"cues":[{"time":242753,"text":"From that came a lot of insights,"},{"time":244649,"text":"or outsights, as I called them,"},{"time":246146,"text":"things that I learned since losing my sight."},{"time":249535,"text":"These outsights ranged from the trival"},{"time":252502,"text":"to the profound,"},{"time":254167,"text":"from the mundane to the humorous."},{"time":256735,"text":"As an architect, that stark juxtaposition"},{"time":259752,"text":"of my sighted and unsighted experience"},{"time":262266,"text":"of the same places and the same cities"},{"time":264551,"text":"within such a short period of time"},{"time":266564,"text":"has given me all sorts of wonderful outsights"},{"time":268770,"text":"of the city itself."},{"time":271944,"text":"Paramount amongst those"},{"time":273818,"text":"was the realization that, actually,"},{"time":275812,"text":"cities are fantastic places for the blind."},{"time":279752,"text":"And then I was also surprised"},{"time":282073,"text":"by the city's propensity for kindness and care"},{"time":285441,"text":"as opposed to indifference or worse."},{"time":288921,"text":"And then I started to realize that"},{"time":290684,"text":"it seemed like the blind seemed to have"},{"time":292673,"text":"a positive influence on the city itself."},{"time":296742,"text":"That was a little curious to me."}]},{"cues":[{"time":299996,"text":"Let me step back and take a look"},{"time":302556,"text":"at why the city is so good for the blind."},{"time":307918,"text":"Inherent with the training for recovery from sight loss"},{"time":311540,"text":"is learning to rely on all your non-visual senses,"},{"time":315411,"text":"things that you would otherwise maybe ignore."},{"time":318637,"text":"It's like a whole new world of sensory information"},{"time":321182,"text":"opens up to you."},{"time":322631,"text":"I was really struck by the symphony"},{"time":324159,"text":"of subtle sounds all around me in the city"},{"time":327135,"text":"that you can hear and work with"},{"time":328427,"text":"to understand where you are,"},{"time":330309,"text":"how you need to move, and where you need to go."},{"time":333114,"text":"Similarly, just through the grip of the cane,"},{"time":335838,"text":"you can feel contrasting textures in the floor below,"},{"time":339752,"text":"and over time you build a pattern of where you are"},{"time":342186,"text":"and where you're headed."},{"time":343728,"text":"Similarly, just the sun warming one side of your face"},{"time":346620,"text":"or the wind at your neck"},{"time":349449,"text":"gives you clues about your alignment"},{"time":351649,"text":"and your progression through a block"},{"time":353342,"text":"and your movement through time and space."},{"time":356847,"text":"But also, the sense of smell."},{"time":359280,"text":"Some districts and cities have their own smell,"},{"time":361981,"text":"as do places and things around you,"},{"time":365022,"text":"and if you're lucky, you can even follow your nose"},{"time":366814,"text":"to that new bakery that you've been looking for."}]},{"cues":[{"time":370243,"text":"All this really surprised me,"},{"time":371952,"text":"because I started to realize that"},{"time":374957,"text":"my unsighted experienced"},{"time":377510,"text":"was so far more multi-sensory"},{"time":379945,"text":"than my sighted experience ever was."},{"time":382970,"text":"What struck me also was how much the city"},{"time":385710,"text":"was changing around me."},{"time":387342,"text":"When you're sighted,"},{"time":389079,"text":"everybody kind of sticks to themselves,"},{"time":391268,"text":"you mind your own business."},{"time":393081,"text":"Lose your sight, though,"},{"time":394348,"text":"and it's a whole other story."},{"time":397147,"text":"And I don't know who's watching who,"},{"time":398626,"text":"but I have a suspicion that\na lot of people are watching me."},{"time":402175,"text":"And I'm not paranoid, but everywhere I go,"},{"time":404323,"text":"I'm getting all sorts of advice:"},{"time":407352,"text":"Go here, move there, watch out for this."},{"time":409672,"text":"A lot of the information is good."},{"time":411749,"text":"Some of it's helpful. A lot of it's kind of reversed."},{"time":414235,"text":"You've got to figure out what they actually meant."},{"time":417804,"text":"Some of it's kind of wrong and not helpful."},{"time":421357,"text":"But it's all good in the grand scheme of things."}]},{"cues":[{"time":424368,"text":"But one time I was in Oakland"},{"time":425904,"text":"walking along Broadway, and came to a corner."},{"time":428791,"text":"I was waiting for an audible pedestrian signal,"},{"time":431598,"text":"and as it went off, I was just about\nto step out into the street,"},{"time":434084,"text":"when all of a sudden, my right hand"},{"time":436116,"text":"was just gripped by this guy,"},{"time":437796,"text":"and he yanked my arm\nand pulled me out into the crosswalk"},{"time":440208,"text":"and was dragging me out across the street,"},{"time":441882,"text":"speaking to me in Mandarin."},{"time":444134,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":445542,"text":"It's like, there was no escape\nfrom this man's death grip,"},{"time":449681,"text":"but he got me safely there."},{"time":451404,"text":"What could I do?"},{"time":453754,"text":"But believe me, there are more polite ways"},{"time":455550,"text":"to offer assistance."},{"time":457723,"text":"We don't know you're there,"},{"time":459245,"text":"so it's kind of nice to say \"Hello\" first."},{"time":461225,"text":"\"Would you like some help?\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":463361,"text":"But while in Oakland, I've really been struck by"},{"time":466412,"text":"how much the city of Oakland changed"},{"time":469030,"text":"as I lost my sight."},{"time":471532,"text":"I liked it sighted. It was fine."},{"time":473699,"text":"It's a perfectly great city."},{"time":476275,"text":"But once I lost my sight"},{"time":477544,"text":"and was walking along Broadway,"},{"time":479859,"text":"I was blessed every block of the way."}]},{"cues":[{"time":483070,"text":"\"Bless you, man.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":484624,"text":"\"Go for it, brother.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":486887,"text":"\"God bless you.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":488637,"text":"I didn't get that sighted."},{"time":490497,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":491833,"text":"And even without sight,\nI don't get that in San Francisco."},{"time":498158,"text":"And I know it bothers some of my blind friends,"},{"time":501150,"text":"it's not just me."},{"time":502743,"text":"Often it's thought that"},{"time":504792,"text":"that's an emotion that comes up out of pity."},{"time":507936,"text":"I tend to think that it comes\nout of our shared humanity,"},{"time":511049,"text":"out of our togetherness, and I think it's pretty cool."},{"time":514159,"text":"In fact, if I'm feeling down,"},{"time":516019,"text":"I just go to Broadway in downtown Oakland,"},{"time":517927,"text":"I go for a walk, and I feel better like that,"},{"time":520586,"text":"in no time at all."}]},{"cues":[{"time":523857,"text":"But also that it illustrates how"},{"time":525892,"text":"disability and blindness"},{"time":527674,"text":"sort of cuts across ethnic, social,"},{"time":530394,"text":"racial, economic lines."},{"time":533120,"text":"Disability is an equal-opportunity provider."},{"time":536955,"text":"Everybody's welcome."},{"time":539398,"text":"In fact, I've heard it said in the disability community"},{"time":541959,"text":"that there are really only two types of people:"},{"time":544461,"text":"There are those with disabilities,"},{"time":546220,"text":"and there are those that haven't\nquite found theirs yet."},{"time":550882,"text":"It's a different way of thinking about it,"},{"time":553003,"text":"but I think it's kind of beautiful,"},{"time":555252,"text":"because it is certainly far more inclusive"},{"time":557428,"text":"than the us-versus-them"},{"time":559533,"text":"or the abled-versus-the-disabled,"},{"time":562101,"text":"and it's a lot more honest and respectful"},{"time":564879,"text":"of the fragility of life."}]},{"cues":[{"time":568183,"text":"So my final takeaway for you is"},{"time":570108,"text":"that not only is the city good for the blind,"},{"time":574176,"text":"but the city needs us."},{"time":577355,"text":"And I'm so sure of that that"},{"time":579393,"text":"I want to propose to you today"},{"time":580989,"text":"that the blind be taken as\nthe prototypical city dwellers"},{"time":584429,"text":"when imagining new and wonderful cities,"},{"time":587714,"text":"and not the people that are thought about"},{"time":589575,"text":"after the mold has already been cast."},{"time":591808,"text":"It's too late then."},{"time":594861,"text":"So if you design a city with the blind in mind,"},{"time":598045,"text":"you'll have a rich, walkable network of sidewalks"},{"time":602630,"text":"with a dense array of options and choices"},{"time":604744,"text":"all available at the street level."},{"time":608176,"text":"If you design a city with the blind in mind,"},{"time":610498,"text":"sidewalks will be predictable and will be generous."},{"time":613618,"text":"The space between buildings will be well-balanced"},{"time":615971,"text":"between people and cars."},{"time":619410,"text":"In fact, cars, who needs them?"},{"time":623467,"text":"If you're blind, you don't drive. (Laughter)"},{"time":626552,"text":"They don't like it when you drive. (Laughter)"},{"time":629915,"text":"If you design a city with the blind in mind,"},{"time":632625,"text":"you design a city with a robust,"},{"time":635268,"text":"accessible, well-connected mass transit system"},{"time":638960,"text":"that connects all parts of the city"},{"time":640562,"text":"and the region all around."},{"time":643581,"text":"If you design a city with the blind in mind,"},{"time":645647,"text":"there'll be jobs, lots of jobs."},{"time":648466,"text":"Blind people want to work too."},{"time":649796,"text":"They want to earn a living."}]},{"cues":[{"time":652235,"text":"So, in designing a city for the blind,"},{"time":654991,"text":"I hope you start to realize"},{"time":657060,"text":"that it actually would be a more inclusive,"},{"time":659938,"text":"a more equitable, a more just city for all."},{"time":663544,"text":"And based on my prior sighted experience,"},{"time":665764,"text":"it sounds like a pretty cool city,"},{"time":667742,"text":"whether you're blind, whether you have a disability,"},{"time":671089,"text":"or you haven't quite found yours yet."}]},{"cues":[{"time":673573,"text":"So thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":676185,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}